bb3b8","parent":"> **このアプリの機能・要件**","children":[{"type":"bulleted_list_item","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-8158-843e-c66b21916e82","parent":"- **数字を表示する部分**（`ft.Text`コントロール）、**「プラス」ボタン**（`ft.FilledTonalButton`コントロール）、**「リセット」ボタン**（`ft.FilledTonalButton`コントロール）の3つで構成される。","children":[]},{"type":"bulleted_list_item","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-818a-b316-e93542725027","parent":"- 各コントロールの並べ方に特に指定はない（横並びでもいい）","children":[]},{"type":"bulleted_list_item","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-8187-b8e8-e51e90dc6480","parent":"- 「プラス」ボタンをクリックすると、数字が１ずつ増える。","children":[]},{"type":"bulleted_list_item","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-8137-8bf5-dcbc706e27a6","parent":"- 「リセット」ボタンをクリックすると、数字が０に戻る。","children":[]}]},{"type":"toggle","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-81d8-95b4-f3785e725ef4","parent":"ヒント1","children":[{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-8130-9d78-c20e27e93572","parent":"各ボタンには`on_click`プロパティを設定する必要があります。","children":[]}]},{"type":"toggle","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-818f-8dbb-d9fa520459c0","parent":"ヒント2","children":[{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-81dd-a2a5-fb24f99386e8","parent":"「プラス」ボタンの`on_click`には数字を増やす`plus_number`関数、「リセット」ボタンの`on_click`には数字を0にする`reset_number`関数を設定するといいでしょう","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-811a-b4cd-db56e77785bf","parent":"（`plus_number`関数と`reset_number`関数は自作する）","children":[]}]},{"type":"toggle","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-81a6-a7ae-de30d4fc2580","parent":"ヒント3","children":[{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-81c3-bb74-e16fc0ccdc22","parent":"`ft.Text`コントロールの表示内容を設定する`value`は文字列型です。そのため、`plus_number`関数の処理内容は少し工夫しなければなりません。","children":[]},{"type":"numbered_list_item","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-8165-958d-f0fce7793450","parent":"1. `ft.Text`コントロールの`value`を整数型に変換して他の変数（例：`num`）に格納","children":[]},{"type":"numbered_list_item","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-81f7-af3c-e4a1095e19c6","parent":"2. `num`を一つ増やす","children":[]},{"type":"numbered_list_item","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-81d5-84ce-c787b6b6000e","parent":"3. `num`を文字列型に変換して、`ft.Text`コントロールの`value`に格納","children":[]},{"type":"numbered_list_item","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-81f8-b106-dd9916785cf6","parent":"4. `ft.Text`コントロールを`update`する","children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-81ae-a449-c941dbbc0cf4","parent":"※ファイルは「flet-prac3.py」として保存","children":[]},{"type":"heading_1","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-81ee-81f5-eefbd65e3b8d","parent":"# 進捗アンケート","children":[]},{"type":"divider","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-819a-9336-fd413f671f23","parent":"---","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-8180-bb33-ce9fe15880df","parent":"この問題が終了した人は、以下のGoogleフォームに回答してください。","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-819e-95b6-c2d0e31afe98","parent":"回答後、練習問題の回答例のURLをメールでお送りします。","children":[]},{"type":"quote","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-8150-92a1-fd43f288375f","parent":"> ","children":[{"type":"bookmark","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-815f-9615-f123bb571545","parent":"[bookmark](https://forms.gle/FFBeAXNS5VA5AJV29)","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"16d0a16d-c518-814e-bbe1-dbb5390e1ac6","parent":"","children":[]}]}],"pageNavs":[{"title":"Home","id":"/posts"},{"title":"基礎班カリキュラム","id":"/posts/course/basic"},{"title":"前期","id":"/posts/course/前期/1"},{"title":"Flet","id":"/posts/post/flet-1"},{"title":"Fletの練習問題3 (1)","id":"/posts/post/flet-116d0a16d-c518-809c-bf96-e1f847d7a915"}],"parentTitle":"Flet","childNavs":[{"title":"6. イベントハンドラと更新 (1)ssssganovnovnaonvo","id":"16d0a16d-c518-8033-8452-d01d97ff8050","child":true},{"title":"Fletの練習問題3 (1)","id":"16d0a16d-c518-809c-bf96-e1f847d7a915","child":true}],"slug":"flet-1","allTags":["基礎班","Python","Flet"]},"__N_SSG":true}